{"id":537468,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/08/深夜走过长安街001｜你是谁操纵的思想火炬/","date":"2016-08-11T02:37:36Z","modified":"2016-08-11T02:37:36Z","title":"深夜走过长安街001｜你是谁操纵的思想火炬","content":"<blockquote style=\"width: 65%;\"><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%8a%b5%e5%88%b6%e8%82%af%e5%be%b7%e5%9f%ba%e7%94%a9%e9%94%85%e6%97%b6%e9%97%b4%e7%ba%bf/\" target=\"_blank\">【立此存照】“抵制肯德基”甩锅时间线</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/%e6%96%87%e4%b8%89%e5%a8%83%ef%bc%9a%e6%9c%b1%e7%bb%a7%e4%b8%9c%e8%80%83/\" target=\"_blank\">文三娃：朱继东考</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/02/%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6%e8%83%8c%e6%99%af%e6%97%b6%e9%97%b4%e7%ba%bf%ef%bc%9a%e6%9c%b1%e7%bb%a7%e4%b8%9c%e6%8a%84%e8%a2%ad%e9%97%a8/\" target=\"_blank\">事件背景时间线：朱继东抄袭门</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>7月13号，随着南海仲裁结果出，新浪微博实名认证账号@朱继东 @新闻为人民 相继发出号召，举国抵制肯德基麦当劳<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npg41jl3j30gh0h6ju1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537498\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npg41jl3j30gh0h6ju1.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6npg41jl3j30gh0h6ju1\" width=\"450\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npg41jl3j30gh0h6ju1.jpg 593w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npg41jl3j30gh0h6ju1-288x300.jpg 288w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后，真的很多地方开始有了现实中的抵制，有人在肯德基门口阻拦欲进店客人，有的在店内骚扰顾客，有的甚至有了暴力&#8230;..</p>\n<p>这时，主流媒体开始向理性爱国引导，有地方公安系统也发出警示，及时止住了朱继东期待的“世界为之哗然”局面的出现。</p>\n<p>但是朱继东及新闻为人民两个账号都已删除了这个帖子，于是有火炬粉继东粉在辩解、甚至有反咬一口说截图是伪造，作为当事人的朱继东本人始终未就此事予以回应。我想，这个举国抵制的倡议是真的，朱继东发出的。</p>\n<p>然后@新闻为人民 发出一个义正辞严的声明，意图把此事与朱继东摘开。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npqr34m6j30ig0djtfa.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537497\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npqr34m6j30ig0djtfa.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6npqr34m6j30ig0djtfa\" width=\"500\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npqr34m6j30ig0djtfa.jpg 664w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6npqr34m6j30ig0djtfa-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>但是，<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nptvsb7fj30go08n3ze.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537496\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nptvsb7fj30go08n3ze.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nptvsb7fj30go08n3ze\" width=\"450\" height=\"233\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nptvsb7fj30go08n3ze.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nptvsb7fj30go08n3ze-300x156.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有意思了。我知道张清在新浪原来有关系，曾帮助不少人搞过认证，那个人因为在微博里辱骂我被我投诉到新浪后被新浪除名了。于是，我知道了，@新闻为人民 居然就是@朱继东 ，更有意思的是@思想火炬 也并非认证的那般唬人是什么国家级部门，而是，@朱继东 。也就是说，朱继东一手握三个认证账号，一个唬人的蓝V，两个很牛叉的黄V。</p>\n<p>其实这也没什么，我也有备用号，比如一个专门发布高考及教育类资讯的，另一个担心哪天说错了话被封的话，的预备，并且是公开告知网友的。</p>\n<p>有意思的是，朱继东手里操作的三个，哦，不是，是四个，还有个粉丝很少的@人民通讯社 ，却是彼此间好不吝惜赞美词汇的对朱继东的打造、吹捧、推荐，甚至公然呼吁习主席重用&#8230;.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq35oev2j30jp09xabt.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537495\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq35oev2j30jp09xabt.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nq35oev2j30jp09xabt\" width=\"400\" height=\"201\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq35oev2j30jp09xabt.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq35oev2j30jp09xabt-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq4n3hznj30ig056jtj.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537494\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq4n3hznj30ig056jtj.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nq4n3hznj30ig056jtj\" width=\"500\" height=\"140\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq4n3hznj30ig056jtj.jpg 664w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq4n3hznj30ig056jtj-300x84.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq59luddj30c80j1n09.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537493\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq59luddj30c80j1n09.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nq59luddj30c80j1n09\" width=\"400\" height=\"623\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq59luddj30c80j1n09.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq59luddj30c80j1n09-193x300.jpg 193w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq5kvpz5j30c80j0gos.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537492\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq5kvpz5j30c80j0gos.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nq5kvpz5j30c80j0gos\" width=\"400\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq5kvpz5j30c80j0gos.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq5kvpz5j30c80j0gos-193x300.jpg 193w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq6iwkroj30c80hbacw.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537491\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq6iwkroj30c80hbacw.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nq6iwkroj30c80hbacw\" width=\"400\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq6iwkroj30c80hbacw.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nq6iwkroj30c80hbacw-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>哦，对了，另一个长期参与吹捧打造朱继东的@北京晓梅 是朱继东的太太，央视七套某栏目编导。</p>\n<p>朱太太从婚后一年就开始对丈夫的名气开始用心的设计，也确实帮了不少忙。毕竟在央视，毕竟资源丰富。<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqieh3ndj30ce0b2n06.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537490\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqieh3ndj30ce0b2n06.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nqieh3ndj30ce0b2n06\" width=\"400\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqieh3ndj30ce0b2n06.jpg 446w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqieh3ndj30ce0b2n06-300x268.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>央视工作的太太利用很多工作便利让丈夫参与栏目<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqk4w8nij30go0c80v2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537489\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqk4w8nij30go0c80v2.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nqk4w8nij30go0c80v2\" width=\"400\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqk4w8nij30go0c80v2.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqk4w8nij30go0c80v2-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而朱继东也没亏待妻子，他的国家文化安全与建设研究中心理事也给了太太一个位置，还有他的马甲@新闻为人民 。<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns7hxklij30hs0vldk6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537488\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns7hxklij30hs0vldk6.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6ns7hxklij30hs0vldk6\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns7hxklij30hs0vldk6.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns7hxklij30hs0vldk6-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns7hxklij30hs0vldk6-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>那么，这个看着很耀眼唬人的国家文化安全与建设研究中心到底是个什么部门呢？经过核实，这个有着唬人名字的机构属于社科院。但是，<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537487\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1.jpg 1118w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1-188x300.jpg 188w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1-768x1228.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqo038ppj30v21do1d1-640x1024.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这是社科院官网截图，在公开的组织架构里看不到思想火炬认证的研究中心，再经过核实，所谓国家文化安全与建设研究中心属于马院下属马研院的再下属挂靠，属 于非实体性研究中心，而这种性质的非实体性研究室，是个社科院的工作人员即能申请，社科院有一百七十多个类似性质的挂靠。</p>\n<p>朱继东的微博简介这样的<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqtz0fcvj30le0gctfq.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537486\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqtz0fcvj30le0gctfq.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nqtz0fcvj30le0gctfq\" width=\"500\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqtz0fcvj30le0gctfq.jpg 770w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqtz0fcvj30le0gctfq-300x229.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqtz0fcvj30le0gctfq-768x586.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>注意划红线这句话：微博为个人观点，不代表新华社、社科院！</p>\n<p>朱继东在济南工作了一年多后调入新华社的，但已于前两年离职，他也不是社科院在编人员，他当然不代表新华社、社科院，这样的写法是故意诱导人们觉得他是新华社和社科院的人吧。</p>\n<p>然后，发现了很多朱继东先生的趣事，比如用三星喊支持国货，<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqz45dmhj30gn0crmyi.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537485\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqz45dmhj30gn0crmyi.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nqz45dmhj30gn0crmyi\" width=\"500\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqz45dmhj30gn0crmyi.jpg 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nqz45dmhj30gn0crmyi-300x230.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>因为我调侃了朱继东的此条心口不一，遭到了朱先生的举报。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr0dgk34j30rp0jptcd.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537484\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr0dgk34j30rp0jptcd.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nr0dgk34j30rp0jptcd\" width=\"550\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr0dgk34j30rp0jptcd.jpg 997w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr0dgk34j30rp0jptcd-300x213.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr0dgk34j30rp0jptcd-768x546.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>只是，我上诉后，朱继东输了。很抱歉。</p>\n<p>朱继东先生的趣事很多，比如知行合一的马克思主义者、中国最出色的意识形态专家也很注意研究其它旁门——<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr2bw0ayj30j60cswh1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537483\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr2bw0ayj30j60cswh1.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nr2bw0ayj30j60cswh1\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr2bw0ayj30j60cswh1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr2bw0ayj30j60cswh1-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr3yky94j30j60gfq60.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537482\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr3yky94j30j60gfq60.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nr3yky94j30j60gfq60\" width=\"400\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr3yky94j30j60gfq60.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr3yky94j30j60gfq60-300x257.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>当然，朱继东先生也很会享受生活，比如能把头等车都包下来——<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr5xcwvtj309804jaab.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537481\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr5xcwvtj309804jaab.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nr5xcwvtj309804jaab\" width=\"332\" height=\"163\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr5xcwvtj309804jaab.jpg 332w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr5xcwvtj309804jaab-300x147.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 332px) 100vw, 332px\" /></a></p>\n<p>朱继东嫉恶如仇，对莆田系对给莆田系提供方便的百度都曾严厉指责。可是，<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8100hij30j61b5thf.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537480\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8100hij30j61b5thf.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nr8100hij30j61b5thf\" width=\"450\" height=\"1107\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8100hij30j61b5thf.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8100hij30j61b5thf-122x300.jpg 122w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8100hij30j61b5thf-416x1024.jpg 416w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8f3kyfj30j60y3q8s.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537479\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8f3kyfj30j60y3q8s.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nr8f3kyfj30j60y3q8s\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8f3kyfj30j60y3q8s.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8f3kyfj30j60y3q8s-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nr8f3kyfj30j60y3q8s-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>更有趣的是，这家爱维艾夫妇科医院的董事长是做建材起家、后做试管奶牛，后来搞试管婴儿——<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nra2e6ojj30cz04fmy5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537478\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nra2e6ojj30cz04fmy5.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nra2e6ojj30cz04fmy5\" width=\"450\" height=\"153\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nra2e6ojj30cz04fmy5.jpg 467w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nra2e6ojj30cz04fmy5-300x102.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>朱太太更是不遗余力为爱维艾夫鼓与呼，要出门做节目都不忘——<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrb1d1rmj30ii0rh44i.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537477\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrb1d1rmj30ii0rh44i.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nrb1d1rmj30ii0rh44i\" width=\"450\" height=\"668\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrb1d1rmj30ii0rh44i.jpg 666w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrb1d1rmj30ii0rh44i-202x300.jpg 202w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后，朱继东夫妻恩爱，还养育了一个神童女儿！————<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrdr9o6qj30j60watdr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537476\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrdr9o6qj30j60watdr.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nrdr9o6qj30j60watdr\" width=\"400\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrdr9o6qj30j60watdr.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrdr9o6qj30j60watdr-178x300.jpg 178w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrdr9o6qj30j60watdr-608x1024.jpg 608w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nre1rui4j30j60wmdlj.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537475\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nre1rui4j30j60wmdlj.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nre1rui4j30j60wmdlj\" width=\"400\" height=\"681\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nre1rui4j30j60wmdlj.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nre1rui4j30j60wmdlj-176x300.jpg 176w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nre1rui4j30j60wmdlj-602x1024.jpg 602w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>小神童出生于2002年，写就这部十六万字长篇时不满十岁。</p>\n<p>更神奇的是，孩子的修辞习惯酷似其母。孩子今天承认微博是母亲替其操作的。孩子的微博，就不截图了。</p>\n<p>九岁小女孩“写就”的十六万字长篇童话小说，第一次就印刷发行了36160册，在当当网一共卖出157本，每本售价14.3元，流水共2245.1元。莫 替人着急，小作者生而有福，其母不但写作修辞习惯酷似小作者，并乃央视7套一栏目编导，节目中打造宣传过的企业家纷纷出手&#8230;..</p>\n<p>关于这本书，问问度娘，太多了。父亲新华社出身、母亲央视，强大的媒体资源厚的让人艳羡。</p>\n<p>作为孩子父亲的朱继东一贯不吝惜对自己及自己家人的赞美，对“女儿的书更是”———<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns38xoqvj30cc09oacz.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537474\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns38xoqvj30cc09oacz.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6ns38xoqvj30cc09oacz\" width=\"444\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns38xoqvj30cc09oacz.jpg 444w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6ns38xoqvj30cc09oacz-300x235.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 444px) 100vw, 444px\" /></a></p>\n<p>思想火炬，你是谁操纵的火炬？无论是谁，希望别往斜路上领人，比如这种令人发指的诅咒和辱骂————<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrmz0s5cj30j40nodiq.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537473\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrmz0s5cj30j40nodiq.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nrmz0s5cj30j40nodiq\" width=\"400\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrmz0s5cj30j40nodiq.jpg 688w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrmz0s5cj30j40nodiq-242x300.jpg 242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>再比如这样的为文革招魂——<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrn99eu0j30i90jptdj.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537472\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrn99eu0j30i90jptdj.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nrn99eu0j30i90jptdj\" width=\"400\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrn99eu0j30i90jptdj.jpg 657w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrn99eu0j30i90jptdj-278x300.jpg 278w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>朱继东先生，你想过没有，如果文革，你的很多言论结果会如何？比如——<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nroyisu0j30gl069750.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537471\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nroyisu0j30gl069750.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nroyisu0j30gl069750\" width=\"500\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nroyisu0j30gl069750.jpg 597w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nroyisu0j30gl069750-300x113.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>再比如———<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrqfy6s3j30c80j1n0a.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537470\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrqfy6s3j30c80j1n0a.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nrqfy6s3j30c80j1n0a\" width=\"400\" height=\"623\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrqfy6s3j30c80j1n0a.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nrqfy6s3j30c80j1n0a-193x300.jpg 193w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这有个专属名词：僭越</p>\n<p>朱继东先生，你僭越的地方不少，比如冒充国家级部门。&#8230;&#8230;.</p>\n<p>朱继东先生，文革好玩吗？贴大字报好玩吗？</p>\n<p>你给别人贴的时候想过别人的感受吗？你私信说你记不得给我贴过大字报搞过围攻，你忘性好大！<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nruu9af4j30gf0judlq.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537469\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nruu9af4j30gf0judlq.jpg\" alt=\"005vSjEdjw1f6nruu9af4j30gf0judlq\" width=\"500\" height=\"604\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nruu9af4j30gf0judlq.jpg 591w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/005vSjEdjw1f6nruu9af4j30gf0judlq-248x300.jpg 248w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>己所不欲勿施于人。朱继东，希望你记住。</p>\n<p>历史的车轮是向前滚动的，朱继东的文革梦只是梦了。但愿。国家，社会，人民，一定会越来越好，人心所向。无论出于什么目的，少些亢奋的忽悠，多些实干吧。爱国，不是只靠喊的。</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[20440,9375,26878,9966,26089]}